f the desire to learn more, what started out as a side project is actually going to be your Superman this summer.</p><p id="0ebd" class="pw-post-body-paragraph nt nu gt nv b hr nw nx ny hu nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo gm bj">With plain JavaScript and an application programming interface (API) call (please use Google here üòâ), we managed to make this possible. I say ‚Äúwe‚Äù because really, every developer has another developer leaning over their shoulder, seeing what they can‚Äôt see, and taking the keyboard for a second or two to create some magic. <em class="op">(To </em><a class="af oq" href="https://twitter.com/codebeast" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><em class="op">Chris</em></a><em class="op"> and </em><a class="af oq" href="https://twitter.com/iChuloo" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><em class="op">William</em></a><em class="op">, thanks a lot guys!)</em></p><p id="a392" class="pw-post-body-paragraph nt nu gt nv b hr nw nx ny hu nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo gm bj">Now lunch is over, let‚Äôs get to building this app‚Ä¶</p><p id="4be8" class="pw-post-body-paragraph nt nu gt nv b hr nw nx ny hu nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo gm bj">We‚Äôve built it already though, just sit back while we walk you through the entire maze. Grab your gear!</p><figure class="nn no np nq nr nm or os paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="ou ov fi ow bg ox"><div class="or os ot"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*4877k4Hq9dPdtmvg9hnGFA.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*4877k4Hq9dPdtmvg9hnGFA.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*4877k4Hq9dPdtmvg9hnGFA.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*4877k4Hq9dPdtmvg9hnGFA.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*4877k4Hq9dPdtmvg9hnGFA.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/