t nv b hr nw nx ny hu nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo gm bj"><em class="op">If you liked this, do click on that little üëè below a few times. Thanks!</em></p></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></article><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg fy fz ga gb"></div></div></div><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg fy fz ga gb"><div class="qh qi ab jq"><div class="qj ab"><a class="qk ax am ao" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/javascript?source=post_page-----3df5ae1fcb27---------------javascript-----------------"><div class="ql fi cw qm gd qn qo be b bf z bj qp">JavaScript</div></a></div><div class="qj ab"><a class="qk ax am ao" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/programming?source=post_page-----3df5ae1fcb27---------------programming-----------------"><div class="ql fi cw qm gd qn qo be b bf z bj qp">Programming</div></a></div><div class="qj ab"><a class="qk ax am ao" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/tech?source=post_page-----3df5ae1fcb27---------------tech-----------------"><div class="ql fi cw qm gd qn qo be b bf z bj qp">Tech</div></a></div><div class="qj ab"><a class="qk ax am ao" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/learning?source=post_page-----3df5ae1fcb27---------------learning-----------------"><div class="ql fi cw qm gd qn qo be b bf z bj qp">Learning</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="l"></div><footer class="qq qr qs qt qu qv qw qx qy ab q qz ja c"><div class="l ae"><div class="ab ca"><div class="ch bg fy fz ga gb"><div class="ab co ra"><div class="ab q ll"><div class="rb l"><span class="l rc rd re e d"><div class="ab q ll"><div class="pw-multi-vote-icon fi ju lm ln lo"><div class=""><div class="lp lq lr ls lt lu lv am lw lx ly lo"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-label="clap"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M11.37.83L12 3.28l.63-2.45h-1.26zM15.42 1.84l-1.18-.39-.34 2.5 1.52-2.1zM9.76 1.45l-1.19.4 1.53 2.1-.34-2.5zM20.25 11.84l-2.5-4.4a1.42 1.42 0 0 0-.93-.64.96.96 0 0 0-.75.18c-.25.19-.4.42-.45.7